properties.media:imagetext:
SOUTH BOUND MENU
BREAKFAST | Flights Departing Before 10 am
FRESH BAKED CINNAMON STREUSEL BREAD
FRUIT PARFAIT WITH POACHED PEARS
Poached pears and cherries tossed in orange blossom honey and
topped with creamy tapioca, crisp rustic granola and fresh mint.
Entrees
SCRAMBLED EGGS ON SCALLION BISCUITS
Home style scallion biscuit with sautéed baby spinach and fresh cage
free scrambled eggs topped with a smoky hollandaise sauce. Country
ham and roasted tomatoes.
CHILAQUILES
Fresh corn tortillas layered with sweet potatoes, corn, red pepper,
grilled chayote squash, poblano chilies, tomatillos, sour cream and
jack cheese. Grilled squash, peppers and asparagus. Gremolata of
choodeo decors. temon. cotd cheese due tresn neros. 00 dno
cream and chipotle oil.
LUNCH AND DINNER | Flights Departing after 10 am
Soft Pretzel Stick and 7 Grain Roll
Entrees
TEQUILA & LIME GLAZED BEEF FILET
Grilled filet of beef glazed with tequila and lime, Cotija stuffed
potatoes, black beans, haricot vert. Sweet corn and cumin coulis
and warm fruit salsa.
TRUFFLE WILD MUSHROOM AND POTATO PAVE
Lavers of thin sliced potatoes, sauteed shitake, ovster. crimini and
domestic mushrooms with fresh herbs and truffles. Tomato coulis,
vegetable ribbons, herb oil and fried basil.
DESSERT
CHOCOLATE MACADAMIA NUT CAKE
Rich chocolate macadamia nut cake. Orange and coconut emulsion.
chocolate sauce and macadamia nut brittle.
SNACKS | Available anytime. Snacks vary per flight.
Ask your in-flight team for today's selections.
WINES | Selections vary
White Wines
CLINE CELLARS VIOGNIER 2008
BUEHLER VINEYARDS RUSSIAN RIVER CHARDONNAY 2008
KARMA Sparkling Wine
A fashion-forward brut, built for the trendiest nightclubs and
lounges but with the refreshing subtlety of melon and pear.
Red wines
PERRIN RESERVE COTES DU RHONE 2007
LOS CARDOS MALBEC 2008
DRINKS
ABSOLUT VODKA
BOMBAY SAPPHIRE GIN
JACK DANIEL'S
THE GLENLIVIT 12 YEAR OLD SCOTCH
BACARDI RUM
BAILEYS IRISH CREAM
VEE V AÇAI SPIRIT
Enjoy the world's first spirit made from the Brazilian superfruit, açaí.
SAUZA HORNITOS REPOSADO
A fine tequila aged in wood barrels, with a golden agave sensation
that's perfect for sipping.
BEER
BLACK STAR BEER
Black Star Double Hopped Golden Lager is hopped first in the kettle
then again detore tinisning. Resurt! A retreshing deer with TOtS OT
taste.
21ST AMENDMENT IPA
From San Francisco local brewery 21st Amendment comes an aromatic
golden brew with a sucker punch of six different hops, quickly balan-
ced by a solid malt back bone.
HEINEKEN
BUD LIGHT
